  "type": "mcq",
  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">If <span class=\"italic\">a</span> and <span class=\"italic\">c</span> are positive numbers, which of the following is equivalent to <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"the square root of, open parenthesis, a plus c, close parenthesis, cubed, end root, times, the square root of a plus c, end root\"></span></span>?</p>\n",
